*konversation-1.0.1-r4 (20 Oct 2007)

  20 Oct 2007; Wulf C. Krueger <philantrop@gentoo.org>
  +files/konversation-1.0.1-serverlist-compiz-workaround.patch,
  -konversation-1.0.1.ebuild, -konversation-1.0.1-r1.ebuild,
  -konversation-1.0.1-r2.ebuild, +konversation-1.0.1-r4.ebuild:
  Added an upstream patch that fixes a problem where there's a broken and
  unclosable server list window hanging around when Konversation is used in
  compiz/beryl. Thanks, Eike, for providing it! Removed obsolete versions.

